content: My name is Vishal Shakya. I am passionate about technology, software development, and artificial intelligence. I enjoy learning new things and building meaningful projects.
I come from a supportive family. My father is Vinod Kumar Shakya and my mother is Babli Devi.
I completed my Bachelor of Science degree, which helped me build a strong foundation in analytical and scientific thinking.
I completed my MCA in Computer Science, where I developed strong skills in software development and problem solving.
I enjoy programming and mainly work with JavaScript, Node.js, and React.
I use HTML and CSS to build clean and responsive user interfaces.
I am deeply interested in AI, especially working with LLMs and building RAG-based systems.
I work as a full-stack developer, handling both frontend and backend development.

I worked on the project "Blockchain eCommerce Platform". I built a blockchain-integrated eCommerce platform focused on secure and transparent transactions. This project strengthened my understanding of decentralized systems.
I worked on the project "Online Examination System". I developed an online examination system with features like timers, auto-evaluation, and result generation.
My long-term dream is to become a Computer Science professor and contribute to education and research.
My career goal is to Become a Computer Science Professor.
I try to code daily and continuously improve my technical skills.
I stay physically active by running daily and playing football.
I focus on self-growth by reading and working on personal projects.
In my free time, I enjoy coding, playing football, learning about AI, and cooking.
